snippet.title: Mischief Motors - Demo Reel
snippet.description:
Mischief Motors is an upcoming game made by a solo developer (me!) inspired by Car combat games like Twisted Metal and Vigilante 8 with a Cartoony style. Not shown in the video but you can also take flight à la Rocket League to get the jump on enemies or to navigate the map faster!

Wishlit me on Steam! (will add the link soon, after verification has passed!)
